<br>
So in zones like Sol B, my effectiveness is reduced because, even when I malaise the kobolds (dark blue con), they still have a good chance of partially/fully resisting my fire based nukes.  Shock of Swords almost always lands for max damage against the kobolds, even if I don't malaise them first.  I have to wait until I'm level 44 and get the conjuration nuke upgrade before I can return to full nuking effectiveness in Sol B.  <br>
<br>
If Verant gave us cold based nukes/bolts at the same level, costing the same amount of mana, inflicting the same amount of damage as our fire based spells, and evocation based, then someone please explain to me how that would overpower us?  The only thing it would do is allow us to be fully effective in more zones, which gives us more places to hunt without overpowering the class.<br>
<br>
Kebkin<br>
Firiona Vie<br>
